import {Link} from 'react-router-dom'

export default function Headers(){
  return(
    <header>
        <Link to="https://github.com/ruturaj-gh" className="logo">
          Blog
        </Link>
        <nav>
        <Link to="/login">Login</Link>
        <Link to="/register">Register</Link> 
        </nav>
      </header>
  )
}
